\n| Team=Giants\n| DrivePlays=\n| DriveLength=\n| DriveTime=\n| Type=FG\n| yards=26\n| Kicker=[[Raul Allegre|Allegre]]\n| Visitor=24\n| Home=55\n}}\n{{AmFootballScoreSummaryEnd|Visitor=24|Home=55}}\n\n===Standings===\n{{1986 NFC East standings}}\n\n==Playoffs==\n\n===Schedule===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"12\" style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New York Giants}} |Post season\n|-\n! Round || Date || Time || Opponent || Result || Giants points || Opponents || Game site || Attendance  || Network TV || National Radio\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fff;\"\n| NFC Wild Card || colspan=11 align=center|''[[Bye (sports)|Bye week]]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"\n| NFC Divisional || January 4, 1987 || 12:30 PM [[Eastern Time Zone|EST]] || [[1986 San Francisco 49ers season|San Francisco 49ers]] || Win || 49 || 3 || [[Giants Stadium]] || <center>76,034</center> || [[NFL on CBS|CBS]] || [[NFL on NBC Radio|NBC]]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"\n| NFC Championship || January 11, 1987 || 4:00 PM [[Eastern Time Zone|EST]] || [[1986 Washington Redskins season|Washington Redskins]] || Win || 17 || 0 || [[Giants Stadium]] || <center>76,633</center> || [[NFL on CBS|CBS]] || [[NFL on NBC Radio|NBC]]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"\n| Super Bowl XXI || January 25, 1987 || 6:00 PM [[Eastern Time Zone|EST]] || [[1986 Denver Broncos season|Denver Broncos]] || Win || 39 || 20 || [[Rose Bowl (stadium)|Rose Bowl]] || <center>101,063</center> || [[NFL on CBS|CBS]] || [[NFL on NBC Radio|NBC]]\n|}\n\n====Post season Game Officials====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"11\" style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New York Giants}} |Game Officials\n|-\n! Week || Opponent || Referee || Umpire || Head Linesman || Line Judge || Back Judge || Side Judge || Field Judge || Replay || Alternate\n|-\n!<center>NFC Wild Card</center>\n| colspan=10 align=center|''[[Bye (sports)|Bye week]]\n|--style=\"background: #ddffdd;\"\